reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice sturdy lamp!
reviews.reviewText: I love this lamp! I like the string on/off switch, and the shade is a perfect style for a nice warm glow in the room at night. If I remember correctly, I had to buy my own lightbulb, so I went with a warmer light for the evening. The picture says it all - sturdy, useful, and a great design.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Cute light, minimal modern design. Smaller than I expected but works great

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love this lamp - going 2 years strong
reviews.reviewText: I've had this as my desk lamp in my home office for the last two years. It just popped up in old orders so I thought I'd write a review. It puts out a lot of light, probably because the shade is light. It's sturdy. And I love the little pull chain to turn it on and off. Couldn't be happier. I bought another lamp at an in person store for my in office office, and I wish I had just ordered a second one of these.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 6, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Very cute! Trendy light wood, pretty much like the pic. Only small difference is the shade is more white when on, even with low wattage bulb. Small enough to fit under my top cupboard. Looks cute with amazon wood kleenex holder.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 25, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Came in perfect condition, looks great, and would highly recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 24, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Simple and Elegant
reviews.reviewText: No gimmicks, just a decently good looking lamp with an on-off toggle.If you like the look of a linen drum to diffuse a light source, this does the job well.The price is reasonable, and the lamp itself is nothing fancy. However there are some little details that go unnoticed that should be mentioned.For starters, the bottom is coated with a non-slip and non-scratch felt or suede covering, this is a nice touch. Also the lamp has a weighted base to it be prevent you from accidentally knocking it over. It's a small thing, but it makes a significant difference.Consider also, the lamp shade is of a fairly standard 1.5ish inch diameter. You do have the ability to replace or upgrade the shade portion independently of the lamp if you want to try something that might suit your aesthetic tastes better.And finally, they offer a decent variety of finishes. I cannot recall the number of times I've found a product that I've liked only to wonder "I wish they made this in a different color."I've liked it enough to order 3 (all in separate orders). Time will tell how it holds up, but I have a feeling there will be no problem.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very small, but love the look
reviews.reviewText: These lamps were much smaller than I realized, but I love the minimalist, contemporary look, so am very happy with them. They are perfect for our nightstands.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice addition to the bedroom.

reviews.reviewText: Really nice lamps. Great price, they look good and are remarkably sturdy. 2 prong plug on top and 2 usb plugs on side, really convenient. Pull chain for on and off. They come assembled which is nice. Unwrap the shades, turn them around and, viola, 2 great lamps. Not very tall, I knew this when I bought them. Description is correct, so don’t complain that they are small. I’ve had compliments on them from my guests. Id definitely buy again.
Lamps were surprisingly great quality and usb charger was a great bonus.
Love this lamp. Goes well with the industrial / rustic look. Keeps the room very well lit too for a night lamp.

reviews.reviewTitle: Great Quality, great price. Thank you.
reviews.reviewText: I just wish the base was a bit heavier. Otherwise, great lamps!
